Parliament’s presiding officers are to brief the media on the State of Readiness for the State of the Nation Address (SONA). Parliament’s Presiding Officers led by the National Assembly Speaker Thandi Modise and National Council of Provinces Chairperson Amos Masondo will provide details about all aspects of the 6th Parliament’s State of resdiness to host SONA by the Head of State. The June 20 SONA is the first for the 6th Parliament of South Africa. 